social_posts.post_text: Happy birthday to my beautiful bestfriend, my sister, my partner in crime. I’ve been gifted the greatest gift, and that’s having you by my side as we tackle life. I’m grateful for all our adventures, our memories and our life experiences. You’ve pulled me out of the darkness and brought me back to light countless times, again and again. You keep me accountable and you give me motivation to continue to better myself on a daily basis. Your words of encouragement lift me up in my lowest, your faith in me gives me faith in my side when I feel absolutely hopeless. You make my world so much more colorful then it’s ever been. I couldn’t imagine doing life without you by my side. You have the most positive energy, genuine and loving heart. I’m home when I’m with you, and when I count my blessings I count you twice🤍 I hope this year is filled with love, happiness and the biggest blessings the world has to offer you. You are the most selfless person I’ve ever known, putting the ones you love always first. I don’t know what I did to deserve a friend as amazing as you, but I’m eternally and forever grateful for you in my life. I love you Boo Boos. HAPPY FREAKINNNN BIRTHDAY SAGITTARIUS QUEEN 🎂🥳
